title: Nikki Glaser Returns
description:
Comedian Nikki Glaser feels chill about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.


 

Nikki sits down with Conan once more to discuss moving back in with her parents, handling criticism, hosting Fboy Island, and pushing the boundaries with her latest special Good Clean Filth.

 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.


 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
